Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.74,0:00:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.47,0:00:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,老師好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.27,0:00:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我高中是你的學生我是水卜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.95,0:00:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是水卜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.28,0:00:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,老師不好意思 很唐突
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,(演出水卜櫻)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.22,0:00:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以打擾你一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.23,0:00:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 天這麼熱你進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.43,0:00:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.58,0:00:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,曾是老實的學生)\N(不穿胸罩的巨乳)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.52,0:01:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,本想讓爸媽高興\N沒想到他們出國旅行去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.26,0:01:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我又沒有鑰匙進不去\N現在沒地方住
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.00,0:01:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒有其他的朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.74,0:01:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都不在 我只能依靠你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.88,0:01:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託你 讓我住到明天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.88,0:01:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,這該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.42,0:01:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,老師拜詆你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.43,0:01:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 隨便你要住多久都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.03,0:01:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,謝射你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.77,0:01:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不過 你要幫忙做些家事\N好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.51,0:01:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不過水卜你變了好多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.18,0:01:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.45,0:02:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,以前很老實反應有點慢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.32,0:02:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,沒想到這麼成熟了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.59,0:02:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,畢業典禮的時候\N老師給了我一些建議
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.52,0:02:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我有說了些甚麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.06,0:02:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你不記得了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.26,0:02:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我說了些甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.80,0:02:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,如果忘了就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.94,0:02:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以告訴我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.52,0:03:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,老師你在看甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.86,0:03:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.52,0:03:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那你打開電腦做甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.73,0:03:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你說這個啊 沒甚麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.27,0:03:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,其實我是找不到檔案
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.41,0:03:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,交給我好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.75,0:03:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,只要按下這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.42,0:03:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,然後再這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.02,0:03:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,接著這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.30,0:04:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,然後再這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.17,0:04:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,然後再按下這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.98,0:04:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,然後把這個畫面儲存起來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.79,0:04:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,老師你有在聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.12,0:04:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我有在聽儲存起來就對了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.73,0:04:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,老師還好你有讓我留下來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.46,0:04:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,說的也是 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.13,0:05:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,老師你在做甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.00,0:05:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事沒甚麼\N真的沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.20,0:05:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是在偷看我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.48,0:05:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.48,0:05:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,老師等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.75,0:06:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,老師不可以這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.96,0:06:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,-對不起 -老師不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.50,0:06:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.30,0:06:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以這樣 老師
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.18,0:06:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,老師老師
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.07,0:06:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不行老師
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.94,0:06:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我忍耐不住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.92,0:07:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.43,0:08:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,老師請住手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.10,0:08:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.66,0:08:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,水卜 剛才真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.60,0:08:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不知道自己怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.73,0:09:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事 別放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.87,0:09:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,真的對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.74,0:09:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,肚子餓了有甚麼吃的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.88,0:09:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有馬上可以吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.21,0:09:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那我來做吧 我很會做菜的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.62,0:09:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那就麻煩你了\N冰箱的東西盡量拿去用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.29,0:09:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.40,0:10:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,老師你在看甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.67,0:10:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,水卜 很抱歉\N我知道這樣不對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.15,0:10:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.62,0:10:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.62,0:10:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.23,0:10:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,住手老師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.37,0:10:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你在做甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.57,0:10:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我要做烏龍面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.71,0:10:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,原來是這樣才會流這麼多汗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.46,0:11:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我無法忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.74,0:11:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我好想這樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.29,0:11:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.43,0:11:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,滿身大汗了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.90,0:11:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.82,0:12:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,老師不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.49,0:12:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.76,0:12:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你的身體令我無法忍受
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.20,0:13:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,老師不可以這樣弄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.80,0:13:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我的身體不聽使喚了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.10,0:14:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 這樣會跑出來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.92,0:14:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,老師不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.92,0:14:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 但很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.23,0:15:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,老師不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.14,0:15:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我忍耐不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.27,0:15:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你做甚麼老師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.02,0:15:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我弄一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.29,0:16:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,老師你做甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.36,0:16:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,老師等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.28,0:16:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.58,0:17:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以老師
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.62,0:18:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.96,0:18:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.63,0:18:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.41,0:19:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 夾一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.81,0:19:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,像這 樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.76,0:20:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你太性感了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.56,0:20:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,老師究竟怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.30,0:20:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.80,0:22:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.10,0:22:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.00,0:23:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,水卜真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.14,0:23:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.81,0:23:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.64,0:28:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,老師你又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.77,0:28:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,水卜對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.84,0:28:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我剛好要停止
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.98,0:28:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.10,0:29:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.90,0:29:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,老師你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.37,0:29:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我聽到你的呼喚
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.28,0:30:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,實在無法壓抑
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.36,0:30:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,為甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.50,0:30:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,就是壓抑不住
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.77,0:30:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,這只是藉口
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.24,0:30:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.05,0:30:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以老師
