Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.76,0:51:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.73,0:52:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.27,0:52:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,老師 這...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.67,0:52:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的壓抑不住
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.70,0:52:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然有點無理\N可以直接這樣進去浴缸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.31,0:53:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,-直接嗎 -對 直接
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.25,0:53:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.46,0:53:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,-會滑動 -沒關絛
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.28,0:53:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,兩邊都握住了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.28,0:53:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,都濕透了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.75,0:53:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.86,0:54:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,水卜你從剛才就一直呻吟\N是很舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.00,0:54:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.07,0:54:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,可是你一直呻吟
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.01,0:54:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.68,0:54:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我明明有聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.15,0:54:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是因為被你嚇到了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.29,0:54:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.65,0:55:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.95,0:56:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,老師 我都濕了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.96,0:56:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你想做甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.83,0:56:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,反正都已經到這個地步了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.83,0:57:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.85,0:58:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,摸到下麵了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.32,0:58:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,青停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.06,0:59:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡也都濕答答的
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.00,0:59:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定很舒服吧\N我沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.01,0:59:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,難道這是尿嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.61,0:59:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.42,0:59:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那讓老師幫你看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.96,0:59:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.30,0:59:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.62,1:00:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服嗎 這裡也洗一下
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.96,1:00:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.65,1:01:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,腳抬起來
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.65,1:01:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,直接這樣沖水
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.27,1:01:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,老師不可以
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.37,1:01:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,吃我
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.35,1:02:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,太舒服了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.75,1:03:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,奶頭都硬了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.30,1:05:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,站起來
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.70,1:05:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.70,1:05:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你要做甚麼
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.52,1:05:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.11,1:06:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.23,1:08:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,趴下
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.18,1:08:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.54,1:09:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.35,1:11:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.56,1:13:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我快要出來了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.10,1:14:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,要出來了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.53,1:14:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,又射了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.24,1:15:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,這個時間有甚麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.38,1:15:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,水卜
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.13,1:15:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.39,1:16:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,水卜 這樣舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.73,1:16:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎 老師很開心
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.46,1:17:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以舔嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.27,1:17:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.41,1:18:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以這樣舔嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.02,1:18:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,可以再往下壓嗎\N好
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.96,1:18:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服 老師\N這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.05,1:18:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊也往下壓
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.19,1:18:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.20,1:19:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-舒服嗎 -對
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.81,1:19:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好溫暖 你舒服嗎\N是
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.18,1:19:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,老師你變大了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.85,1:19:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我幫你夾吧
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.19,1:20:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你願意幫我夾嗎\N對
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.93,1:20:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那你幫我夾
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.75,1:20:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,-請你幫我夾 -好
Dialogue: 0,1:20:52.18,1:20:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,老師感覺如何
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.85,1:20:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,非常舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.58,1:20:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.62,1:21:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,水卜 你為何願意這樣做
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.36,1:21:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,這是我的秘密
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.30,1:21:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊 不過好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.84,1:22:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣如何\N非常舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.82,1:22:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好像快出來了
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.57,1:23:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,老師 忍耐久一點會更舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:23:05.31,1:23:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.25,1:23:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你為何願意幫我這樣做\N這是我的秘密
Dialogue: 0,1:23:46.55,1:23:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,老師舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.89,1:23:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.56,1:23:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.51,1:24:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.58,1:24:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,要出來了
Dialogue: 0,1:24:21.65,1:24:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,多忍耐一下 會更爽的
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.06,1:24:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,還要我忍耐嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:24:45.94,1:24:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.69,1:25:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,希望能讓你更舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.36,1:25:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.37,1:25:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.12,1:25:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,真的快要出來了
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.06,1:25:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,要出來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.54,1:25:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:26:05.49,1:26:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.46,1:26:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,射出來好多
Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.06,1:26:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,太舒服了
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.00,1:26:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,可是水卜為何要這麼做
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.80,1:26:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,這是我的秘密
Dialogue: 0,1:26:57.94,1:27:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不能說嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.88,1:27:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,媽 你們回來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.69,1:27:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,既然你們在家 那我等等回去
Dialogue: 0,1:27:19.70,1:27:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,1:28:14.02,1:28:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你要回去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:28:17.29,1:28:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,對 因為爸媽已經回家了
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.89,1:28:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,1:28:23.76,1:28:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那個..老師\N怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.30,1:28:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,請再跟我做愛
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.84,1:28:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,老師說我以前是個老實的學生
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.45,1:28:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我從小因為胸部太大\N心中總是有陰影
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.46,1:28:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊 很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.93,1:29:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,老師在串業典禮後\N曾經對我說
Dialogue: 0,1:29:03.80,1:29:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,能夠超越自己的只有自己
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.54,1:29:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,要做自己愛自己
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.41,1:29:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,從那時起\N我才開始敢穿自己想穿的衣服
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.82,1:29:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你還要我別把自己包得太緊
Dialogue: 0,1:29:24.42,1:29:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,可能我說過吧
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.52,1:30:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不過水卜我當時說的\N並不是指衣服
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.13,1:30:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.47,1:30:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不過老師你毫不掩飾\N讓我很吃驚
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.68,1:31:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,老師多摸我一些
Dialogue: 0,1:31:35.49,1:31:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:32:56.70,1:32:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,老師 好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:33:00.10,1:33:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:34:08.64,1:34:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,腳拾起來
Dialogue: 0,1:35:18.44,1:35:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你都瀑了 還一直抖動
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.46,1:35:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:36:21.17,1:36:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,老師多弄我一些
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.46,1:36:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,怎陛了
Dialogue: 0,1:36:52.80,1:36:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,請舔我
Dialogue: 0,1:38:09.61,1:38:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,老師吻我
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.57,1:40:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.35,1:41:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,過來這裡
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.69,1:41:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,-舔我的奶頭 -好
Dialogue: 0,1:42:46.49,1:42:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服\N我也很舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:43:18.39,1:43:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我想吃老師的老二
Dialogue: 0,1:43:21.59,1:43:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你要幫我舔嗎\N對
Dialogue: 0,1:44:15.64,1:44:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,太舒服了
Dialogue: 0,1:44:45.14,1:44:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服吧\N對
Dialogue: 0,1:44:48.94,1:44:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,用老二摩擦一下胸部\N好的
Dialogue: 0,1:45:03.16,1:45:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,奶頭好舒服\N我也很舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:45:13.50,1:45:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:45:41.80,1:45:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:45:56.48,1:45:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,把衣服拉起來
Dialogue: 0,1:46:04.75,1:46:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,太爽了
Dialogue: 0,1:46:17.90,1:46:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我忍耐不住了
Dialogue: 0,1:46:21.44,1:46:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,可以插進來嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:46:25.64,1:46:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我也好想要
Dialogue: 0,1:46:29.91,1:46:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,要放進去了
Dialogue: 0,1:46:47.33,1:46:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:46:49.66,1:46:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,1:47:22.16,1:47:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,老師 我好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:47:39.58,1:47:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,出來了
Dialogue: 0,1:47:55.80,1:47:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以看得好清楚
Dialogue: 0,1:47:58.40,1:48:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,太舒服了
Dialogue: 0,1:48:20.42,1:48:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,出來了
Dialogue: 0,1:48:50.52,1:48:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你很快就高潮
Dialogue: 0,1:48:54.52,1:48:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,因為老二插入太舒服了
Dialogue: 0,1:49:08.00,1:49:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,出來了
Dialogue: 0,1:49:41.24,1:49:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,太舒服了
Dialogue: 0,1:50:31.29,1:50:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,出來了
Dialogue: 0,1:51:08.79,1:51:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,又要出來了
Dialogue: 0,1:51:21.00,1:51:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,1:51:57.24,1:51:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,插到底部好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:52:00.71,1:52:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我也很舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:52:53.29,1:52:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:53:00.70,1:53:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,出來了
Dialogue: 0,1:53:59.56,1:54:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,太舒服了
Dialogue: 0,1:54:22.45,1:54:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,太舒服了
Dialogue: 0,1:54:41.47,1:54:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,出來了
Dialogue: 0,1:55:00.36,1:55:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,出來了
Dialogue: 0,1:55:09.76,1:55:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:55:12.97,1:55:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,1:55:21.31,1:55:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,奶子跟陰部都好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:55:44.93,1:55:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,出來了
Dialogue: 0,1:56:33.85,1:56:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,1:56:57.41,1:56:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,出來了
Dialogue: 0,1:57:19.23,1:57:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,吃我的胸部
Dialogue: 0,1:57:39.11,1:57:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服嗎\N很舒服老師
Dialogue: 0,1:57:49.52,1:57:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,太舒服了
Dialogue: 0,1:57:59.40,1:58:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,-舒服嗎 -舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:58:43.64,1:58:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我要射精了
Dialogue: 0,1:59:23.35,1:59:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,1:59:26.09,1:59:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我好愛你
